00:48:14.100 --> 00:48:17.420
that trading idea works, or that
approach to the markets work,

00:48:17.420 --> 00:48:20.230
but I think in the vast
majority of circumstances--

00:48:20.230 --> 00:48:23.500
I mean, I'm trying to buy
